{"tid":1674242,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【開業一年兩個月】李家鼎餐廳下月結業 難敵經營壓力上升","createTime":"2019-10-25T06:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T05:32:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d2c6a3f6f28f11c7ad98c9fef21451b4fb9d9d","tid":1674242,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"煮食節目層出不窮，好多藝人都擔任過主持，不過講到真功夫，就要數「鼎爺」李家鼎的《阿爺廚房》，三輯節目都盡顯功架，甚至有人會諗「鼎爺係咪入錯行？」<br />\n人氣旺，鼎爺食住個勢大展拳腳，接多了廣告又與不少品牌合作。鼎爺之後有進軍飲食業開了3間餐廳，不過「鼎爺私房菜 Ding's Kitchen」今日於facebook宣佈，由於鼎會館經營壓力上升，鼎會館將於下月22日結束營業。根據資料，該餐廳上年9月才開業，不少人都讚食物出色，對結業覺得可惜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191025/large/1571968487_7176.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191025%2Flarge%2F1571968487_7176.jpg&h=1c4dcb75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191024/60192118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F60192118&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=1c093e8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F60192118&h=2a1352c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191024/60192118</a>"},{"pid":"3699bc963c764857ec6d887b68efc53eeba7f605","tid":1674242,"uid":27432,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:12:38.000Z","msg":"平民既食物<br />\n又要行高檔路線"},{"pid":"faa759ab63c27b692a5755da16b62dfe65004c00","tid":1674242,"uid":242537,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:13:40.000Z","msg":"再一次證明<br />\n乜鳩狗屎垃圾<br />\n賣到貴一貴 d港豬仆過去打卡 再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets